<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8"/>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f8fafc;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .email-container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
    }
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FF8C42 0%, #FF6B35 100%);
      padding: 40px 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .header h1 {
      color: #ffffff;
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin: 0;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 40px 30px;
    }
    .greeting {
      font-size: 18px;
      color: #0F172A;
      margin: 0 0 20px 0;
    }
    .text-block {
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #475569;
      margin: 0 0 20px 0;
    }
    .credentials-box {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #F0F9FF 0%, #E0F2FE 100%);
      border-left: 4px solid #3B82F6;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 24px;
      margin: 30px 0;
    }
    .credentials-box h2 {
      color: #1E40AF;
      font-size: 20px;
      margin: 0 0 16px 0;
    }
    .credential-row {
      display: flex;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      align-items: baseline;
    }
    .credential-label {
      color: #64748B;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 14px;
      min-width: 100px;
    }
    .credential-value {
      color: #0F172A;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .password-value {
      background-color: #fff;
      padding: 8px 12px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      border: 1px solid #CBD5E1;
    }
    .cta-button {
      display: inline-block;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FF8C42 0%, #FF6B35 100%);
      color: #ffffff !important;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 16px 32px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 16px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(255, 107, 53, 0.2);
    }
    .cta-button:hover {
      box-shadow: 0 6px 8px rgba(255, 107, 53, 0.3);
    }
    .footer {
      background-color: #f8fafc;
      padding: 30px;
      text-align: center;
      border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    }
    .footer p {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #64748B;
      margin: 0 0 8px 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-container">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Third time is the charm</h1>
    </div>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <div class="content">
      <p class="greeting">Hi <%= @user.name %>!</p>

      <p class="text-block">
        You have now been granted full access to the app. There was a mistake before where we were doing it in development, but now everything is fixed.
      </p>

      <% if @password.present? %>
        <!-- Credentials Box (for new accounts) -->
        <div class="credentials-box">
          <h2>Your Account Information</h2>

          <div class="credential-row">
            <div class="credential-label">Email:</div>
            <div class="credential-value"><%= @user.email %></div>
          </div>

          <div class="credential-row">
            <div class="credential-label">Password:</div>
            <div class="credential-value password-value"><%= @password %></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      <% end %>

      <p class="text-block">
        You should be able to access it via this link and immediately have full access:
      </p>

      <p class="text-block" style="text-align: center; font-size: 18px;">
        <a href="<%= @login_url %>" style="color: #FF6B35; text-decoration: underline; font-weight: 600;"><%= @login_url %></a>
      </p>

      <p class="text-block">
        Again, sorry, startups can be hectic. Thanks for understanding.
      </p>

      <p class="text-block">
        Best,<br>
        <strong>The AI Talk Coach Team</strong>
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Questions? Email us at support@aitalkcoach.com</p>
      <p style="color: #94A3B8; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 16px;">
        AI Talk Coach | Your Communication Partner
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
